  <brief_title>Simultaneous Islet-Kidney Transplantation in Patients of Type 1 Diabetes With End-stage Renal Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>Simultaneous Islet-Kidney Transplantation in Patients of Type 1 Diabetes With End-stage Renal Disease</official_title>
